---
description: Commit message format
alwaysApply: true
---

Conventional Commits:

```text
<type>(<scope>): <subject>
```

Types: `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `style`, `refactor`, `perf`, `test`, `build`, `ci`, `chore`, `revert`, `a11y`.

Common scopes: `preset`, `cli`, `i18n`, `registry`, `docs`, `storybook`, `ci`, `deps`, `repo`.

Subject: imperative, lowercase, no trailing period.

Examples:

```text
feat(registry): add dialog component
fix(preset): correct dark mode semantic tokens
a11y(combobox): add aria-activedescendant for option focus
chore(deps): bump radix-ui
```
